window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Draasin Lord is captured, but a greater threat remains. </b></p> <p>Now that Tolan knows the secret of the Draasin Lord, he recognizes more needs to be done. As a student, he’s not in a position to be able to do more, but as a master shaper, he’d be free to travel as he feels necessary.</p> <p>When another attack targets the academy, Tolan knows his unique abilities might make him the only shaper able to respond.</p> <p>He must survive crossing the waste, but even if he does, how can he stop the chaos where none can shape the elements and where no elementals can survive?</p>"; 
